MADE IN AMERICA: MY STORY

By Sam Walton Doubleday, Dollars 22.50.
Since then, some aspects of Wal-Mart's business - its anti-union policies, the impact of its Dollars 40bn annual sales on hundreds of Mom-and-Pop shops -have been subject to critical scrutiny.
